xp you can always get whenever.  the ability to kill ntov named mobs are allowed only to a very select few of the server population, due to the current game design.  a change of making all ubers random 8-24 hour spawns, and yet keeping drop rates compared to real time the same, allows for more people to at least go after said mobs...<br>
